extendedInfo.description: The brand new running game, Crazy Running, hits on its dynamite debut on your Android Phone!Running Baby takes into a more exciting escaping adventure!You will be a little baby in this game. You escape from a carefully guarded kindergarten and run for your special journey! You have to dodge all kinds of obstacles and policemen on your way.With the longer way you running, your speed will be faster and faster!Show us how long your journey can be!Collecting more coins to get wonderful power-ups and choose the characters that you love! Game Features:-3D graphics with amusing style, you can play it with the first-person view.-Various obstacles and bend tracks challenge your responding speed-easy control and operation help you dive into the fun world-Special and funny game sound.-A various power-ups and game characters are waiting for you.
